<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>
<expan>Vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Karl <expan>Holczschüh<ex>er</ex></expan>. <lb/></ab>
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Wirich, als ir mir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dez <expan>Swelh<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, ist es, daz ir ervaret, was die sach sey, so
                        möht ir wol einen tag machen gen <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gen <expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan>, erfürt
                        ir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> der sache nicht, so macht keinen tag, und
                        was ir tüt, das tüt als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew selbs, als ir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol wisset, wie ir nu
                                <expan>awsgeschied<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seit.</ab>
</div>
